Jude Kuring https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jude_Kuring 0 Judith Kuring (born November 1948) known as Jude Kuring is an Australian actress who appeared in film and television during the late 1970s and early 80s. She remains best known for her role as petty criminal Noeline Bourke in the soap opera Prisoner. Her film roles include The Singer and the Dancer, Journey Among Women, Newsfront, The Journalist, ...Maybe This Time and Prisoner Queen.
